      <title>法国将正式审查 CD&R 收购赛诺菲子公司：Figaro</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/france-to-formally-screen-cd-r-purchase-of-sanofi-unit-figaro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《费加罗报》周一报道称，法国政府正在考虑各种选择，包括让国有投资银行 BPIfrance 入股赛诺菲消费者保健业务的股份，而赛诺菲正就出售该业务与美国收购公司 Clayton Dubilier &amp; Rice 进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/france-to-formally-screen-cd-r-purchase-of-sanofi-unit-figaro</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 09:24:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
